{"tid":2205684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜：港區國安法違反中英聯合聲明 影響言論自由","createTime":"2020-09-17T03:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T10:21:49.000Z","uid":5195,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6fe5b8588e18d201eb286b3fb9caae9ffab63b42","tid":2205684,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:50:58.000Z","msg":"英國首相約翰遜相信，中國在香港實施「港區國安法」，違反《中英聯合聲明》的條文及精神。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜在國會下議院接受議員質詢時表示，「港區國安法」的訂立及實施，已經影響到言論自由，受影響的亦包括英國公民。但約翰遜表示，英國政府未決定是否會杯葛2022年舉行的北京冬季奧運。<br />\n<br />\n訪問華盛頓的英國外相藍韜文，與美國國務卿蓬佩奧舉行會談時，亦討論到香港與新疆問題。藍韜文在記者會上表示，香港及新疆的人權都遭到嚴重侵害，促請中國政府恪守國際承諾，尊重香港人的自由及自治，英方將持續關注國安法的實施，以及所帶來的影響。"},{"pid":"d43225a7e5cc6479dd936837ddb1dc3405024ed4","tid":2205684,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9e79dec3422f046b3f4a4726c85bd9fc279484","tid":2205684,"uid":55955,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"制裁官員未"},{"pid":"d94011f0f0f62eb948257781c26a847c88b77dde","tid":2205684,"uid":18477,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:02:15.000Z","msg":"收返香港"},{"pid":"d0f41f59630c84a8b184febaa298625ae61f5098","tid":2205684,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"Boris日出.gif"},{"pid":"790e1778fd59c0d63ae3ca9d081433836d14e0e5","tid":2205684,"uid":321255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"留名等睇boris日出gif"},{"pid":"424a4da03b73b43d931be87f2e9136ed4204db01","tid":2205684,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"